originalText.text:
If you're looking for an excellent Physician then look no further than doctor Guzman. Doctor Guzman is dependable he is a wonderful trustworthy physician who really cares about his patients. I know this because my father is lucky enough to be one of his patients my father Alberto has been so happy since I found doctor Guzman for him.
He has been in better health than he has ever been before and because of this I wanted to say thank you and write this review. Also the staff is very pleasant and sweet and very helpful and the office is always very clean thank you doctor Guzman for running such a great practice and for being such a great physician.  As for waiting for your appointment it varies sometimes you have to wait less than 15 minutes sometimes a little more but it's always worth it when you're going to see a doctor like doctor Guzman.
